# =============================================================================
# GOVERNANCE FRAMEWORK (Wave 38)
# =============================================================================
# See docs/governance/OWNERSHIP_MODEL.md for complete governance framework:
# - Weekly Service Ownership Reviews (service owner + EM + SRE)
# - Biweekly Contract Reviews (cross-team + data platform)
# - Monthly Reliability Reviews (platform + SRE + leadership)
# - Quarterly Steering (architecture + roadmap)
#
# All CODEOWNERS groups correspond to Slack channels and DRI assignments.
# SLO definitions: docs/slos/service-slos.md (per-service availability + latency)
# Error budgets: docs/adr/015-slo-error-budget-policy.md (multi-window burn rates)
# ADRs: docs/adr/ (all decisions require platform review + principal engineer signoff)
# =============================================================================
